channel.title: Impact - Excitment around every corner~
channel.description:
Impact was a server that I created last February, maybe even January, it was based of the popular server Emulous 1.62. When it began it was supposed to be a little quick pk server. But it grew from its pk server status, in to a project that was developed for about 5-6 months. Around the time of release I decided that I could not put the time and dedication needed in to the server. So I decided to stop the project, the server is just wasting away on my computer when people could use it. So I have decided to release . If you would like to see pictures of the server click (REMOVED BY ME). There are many pictures and videos of the server on that thread.
